ection"><h2 class="about-section-heading">Who <span class="text-span-7">We Are</span></h2><p class="about-paragprah">Christiansen Design are an experienced and qualified architectural design and drafting | draftsman | draughting team.<br/><br/>Incredibly they have over 64 years combined experience in the building industry.<br/><br/>Whether its a new home, subdivision, renovation or alteration to an existing home, they have the knowledge to develop your project to a functional, cost effective solution.<br/><br/>Over the years they have helped many New Zealand home owners, builders and developers achieve their goals.<br/><br/>​Our aim is to provide an affordable service to clients who feel like they don&#x27;t need an expensive registered architect.<br/><br/>Christiansen design believe in communication based on integrity, honesty and transparency.​</p><h2 class="about-section-heading top-margin">Meet the <span class="text-span-7">Team</span></h2><div class="grid-wrapper"><div class="team-grid"><div id="w-node-_49b0399a-3915-0b4c-960d-b0759e6b2fef-bfe1ebe0" class="team-member-wrapper"><div class="flexbox centre nogap"><div class="left-flex _25"><div class="team-m-photo-div max"></div></div><div class="right-flex"><h1 class="heading-6">Max Christiansen</h1></div></div><p class="team-member-paragraph">Max brings 50 years’ experience in the building industry. Working as an architectural designer for housing &amp; commercial projects from renovations, new builds and developments &amp; commercial interiors, Max has also worked as a builder &amp; construction manager and is fluent user of Revit Architecture &amp; AutoCad software.<br/><br/>With his practical experience and construction knowledge Max can deliver innovative design solutions.​<br/><br/>Max is a Licensed Building Practitioner - Design Level 2​</p></div></div></div></section><section class="footer-dark-2"><div class="container-5"><div class="footer-wrapper-2"><a href="#" class="footer-brand-2 w-inline-block"><img